### ============================================================
### Posts
### ============================================================

### Public list of posts
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/posts

### Public single post
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create a post — prepare_post auto-fills created_by and generates slug
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/posts
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello Shaperail",
  "body": "This post was created from the blog-api example.",
  "status": "draft"
}

### Create a post — status defaults to "draft" when omitted
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/posts
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Second Post!",
  "body": "Status will default to draft because we did not specify it."
}

### Create a post — FAILS: empty body
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/posts
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Post",
  "body": "   "
}

### Update a post — member tries to publish (FAILS: only admins can publish)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "published"
}

### Update a post — admin publishes successfully
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "published"
}

### Update a post — revert published to draft WITHOUT reason header (FAILS)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "draft"
}

### Update a post — revert published to draft WITH reason header (succeeds)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json
X-Edit-Reason: Needs factual corrections before republishing

{
  "status": "draft"
}

### Update a post — title change auto-updates slug
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title Here"
}

### Update an archived post (FAILS: archived posts cannot be edited)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Trying to edit archived"
}

### Delete a post — cleanup_comments adds X-Comments-Archived header
DELETE http://localhost:3000/v1/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

### ============================================================
### Comments
### ============================================================

### List comments for a post
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/comments?filter[post_id]=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### Create a comment on a published post (succeeds)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/comments
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "post_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "body": "Great article!",
  "author_name": "Mahin"
}

### Create a comment on a draft post (FAILS: post_not_published)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/comments
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "post_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "body": "This should fail because the post is still a draft.",
  "author_name": "Mahin"
}

### Create a comment with HTML in body (tags get stripped)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/comments
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "post_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "body": "Nice post! <script>alert('xss')</script> Really enjoyed it.",
  "author_name": "Mahin"
}

### Create a comment — FAILS if body is only HTML tags
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/comments
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "post_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "body": "<script>alert('xss')</script>",
  "author_name": "Mahin"
}

### Update own comment within 15-minute window (succeeds)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Updated my comment."
}

### Update someone else's comment as non-admin (FAILS: 403 Forbidden)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
Authorization: Bearer <other-member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Trying to edit someone else's comment."
}

### Update old comment as non-admin (FAILS: edit_window_expired)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
Authorization: Bearer <member-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "This comment is older than 15 minutes."
}

### Update old comment as admin (succeeds — admins bypass edit window)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Admin can edit any comment regardless of age."
}

### Delete a comment
DELETE http://localhost:3000/v1/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
